Package SixesWildGame.boundary

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Application
    Application - This is the main boundary class, it runs the GUI for the game and switches between panes, as well as acting as the mediator for elements of the game that want access to GUI classes
    BoardView
    BoardView - This is the Boundary class which displays the contents of a Board
    ClockTick
    ClockTick - This is the Boundary class which counts clock ticks for use in the lightning level type
    DefeatScreen
    DefeatScreen - This is the Boundary class which displays the defeat screen
    Deserializer
    Deserializer - This is the boundary class used for loading levels
    ScoreLoad  
    ScoreRecord  
    ScoreSave  
    SelectionMenu
    SelectionMenu - This is the Boundary class which displays the main menu
    selectLevel  
    Serializer
    Serializer - This is the boundary class used for saving levels
    SixesWildGUI
    SixesWildGUI This is the boundary class that displays the pane that the BoardView is displayed on, as well as the buttons that operate the game and the scoreboard for the game itself.
    SplashScreen
    SplashScreen - This is the boundary class which displays the splash screen
    VictoryScreen
    VictoryScreen - This is the Boundary class which displays the victory screen
